Hello, and thanks for downloading my map.

I have been learning to create maps for counter strike, roughly just over a year now. I learned to create through trial and error, as I found most places don't really help that much, they allready expect you to know a great deal.

So I do still have more to learn, and I definatly need to get to grips with taking advantage of the physics engine, but honestly I don't have much time anymore.
